HEADWORD: Approval
<hw>Ap*prov"al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Approbation;
sanction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A censor . . . without whose <qex>approval</qex> no capital
sentences are to be executed.</q> <rj><qau>Temple.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- See <er>Approbation</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
